{"tid":25524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"店員偷錢　自扑扮遇劫","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T21:30:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af0420da2e144f658df25beb2813630ee5b029ba","tid":25524,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856447&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d230ab9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856447&h=d8700075\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856447</a><br />\n<br />\n店員偷錢　自扑扮遇劫<br />\n<br />\n8,109<br />\n ■疑犯在元朗開心廣場一間錶行工作。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■疑犯在元朗開心廣場一間錶行工作。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗一名28歲錶行職員疑賭馬輸錢，前晚替公司入數期間，施展苦肉計，「自編自導自演」搶劫案，企圖私吞公司7,500元營業額。警方調查後發現他涉報假案將他拘捕。<br />\n被捕男子姓劉（28歲），在元朗開心廣場一間錶行工作。前日下午5時許，姓袁（50歲）女店長接獲劉電話，當時劉報稱在青山公路近輕鐵康樂路站附近，遭賊人扑頭搶劫，劫去7,500元。袁趕落樓查看，見劉頭破血流，將他帶回店舖後報警。警到場調查，劉稱當時帶同公司營業額7,500元往銀行入數，因多人輪候就離開返店舖，其間被賊人尾隨扑頭將錢搶走。救護車其後將劉送院治理，之後被帶署助查，警員發現劉說話前後矛盾，嚴詞詰問下，劉承認訛稱遇劫騙財。據悉，有人疑賭馬失利出此下策。姓袁錶行女店長指，涉案男職員入職3年，負責銷售工作，形容他「工作盡責、為人OK」，但私底下不相熟，不清楚其財政狀況。<br />\n■記者黃昇  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n青年為找卡數販毒　母自殺亡"},{"pid":"42e5d1cd0bb8e0a7f794010aeeda6902e75a9277","tid":25524,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161206/large/06la7p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161206%2Flarge%2F06la7p3.jpg&h=0e0d5629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d97921077ab64fe033fecb393f2bfab1e487708c","tid":25524,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"時為7千幾有案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea7326a3c0d08a11cdb2577aca1476b47fdddad","tid":25524,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"比人chok兩野就淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320cd716600babe3dc2552a40626eae6f1171403","tid":25524,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時為7千幾有案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把銀行肯借12倍月薪"},{"pid":"fa32be285d145164dcd37307f0564a56ebad1982","tid":25524,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e182fbee2d399922a2d559d99950984a5aa53de5","tid":25524,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"周熱圍都係cam<br />\n邊到你鳩up"},{"pid":"b19658c887f3e8bd323d1453f1ccb4700a80c9f7","tid":25524,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b837c6f4192b431684551fa07716c05c33e44796","tid":25524,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"扑到自己頭都穿分分鐘坐監得果7千唔死都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb2eb5e5f0d9ac13219920a3383cd28626ac715","tid":25524,"uid":45430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑撚右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1bfc2e617cd7042cba8e57ae6ac2e85aae818d","tid":25524,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislik